title: Divination - Ambient Dub Volume 1 (FLAC)
description:
Divinations first album, Ambient Dub Volume I, was released on Subharmonic in 1993. Teaming up with Liu Sola, Jeff Bova, Nicky Skopelitis, Buckethead and Robert Musso, Bill Laswell created a blend between ethereal ambience and strong house rhythms.
